{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":3,"markdown":"Les indicateurs CPN1 et CPN4 présentent des cycles marqués et évoluent de manière cohérente.

Le TPI3 suit une trajectoire similaire à celle du CPN4, avec un creux marqué au début de 2024, suivi d’un pic en fin d’année avant de redescendre.
","stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false},{"type":"placeholder","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Tendances en soins prénatals","useFooter":false,"footerText":""}}

{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"span":3,"markdown":"Au niveau national, la cohérence est limitée : seulement 47 % des districts présentent un volume d’accouchements équivalent à celui de la BCG, et seulement 28 % un volume de CPN1 supérieur à CPN4.

Pour la vaccination, 60 % des régions ont un volume de Penta1 supérieur à Penta3, en dessous du seuil attendu de 80 %.
"},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"cf5b8649-93c2-4bbe-8f2d-773f42ce8ec3","moduleId":"m001","selectedReplicantValue":"","isDefault":true}}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Cohérence interne"}}

{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"span":3,"markdown":"À l’échelle nationale, la qualité des données reste très faible et en recul, passant de 48 % en 2021 à seulement 30 % en 2025.

La plupart des régions se situent en dessous de 40 % en 2025.

"},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"d46e1957-09dd-41c3-b7dc-b4409da23bbe","moduleId":"m001","selectedReplicantValue":"","isDefault":true}}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Tendances du Score de Qualité des Données (SQD)"}}

